#: ../../manual/compositing/types/filter/defocus.rst:11
msgid "Defocus Node."
msgstr "散焦节点。"

#: ../../manual/compositing/types/filter/defocus.rst:13
msgid "The *Defocus Node* blurs areas of an image based on a map/mask input."
msgstr "*散焦节点* 基于一张 图片/遮罩 输入来模糊相应区域。"

#: ../../manual/compositing/types/filter/defocus.rst:15
msgid "It is typically used to emulate depth of field (:term:`DOF`) using a post-processing method with a Z-buffer input. But also allows to blur images that are not based on Z depth too."
msgstr "此节点一个典型应用是运用Z-缓冲区输入连接端口在后期合成中模拟景深 (:term:`DOF`)效果。当然也可以不连接Z深度通道端口对图像进行模糊操作。"

#: ../../manual/compositing/types/filter/defocus.rst:20
msgid "Inputs"
msgstr "输入"

#: ../../manual/compositing/types/filter/defocus.rst:22 ../../manual/compositing/types/filter/defocus.rst:80
msgid "Image"
msgstr "图像"

#: ../../manual/compositing/types/filter/defocus.rst:23
msgid "Standard image input."
msgstr "标准化图像输入。"

#: ../../manual/compositing/types/filter/defocus.rst:26
msgid "Z"
msgstr "Z通道"

#: ../../manual/compositing/types/filter/defocus.rst:25
msgid "Z-buffer input, but could also be a (grayscale) image used as a mask, or a single value input."
msgstr "Z-缓冲区输入连接端口，可以用一张（灰度）图作为遮罩，或者是一个单独数值作为输入值。"

#: ../../manual/compositing/types/filter/defocus.rst:29
msgid "Properties"
msgstr "属性"

#: ../../manual/compositing/types/filter/defocus.rst:34
msgid "Bokeh Type"
msgstr "散景类型"

#: ../../manual/compositing/types/filter/defocus.rst:32
msgid "The number of iris blades of the virtual camera's diaphragm."
msgstr "模拟摄影机的光圈可变光阑片数量。"

#: ../../manual/compositing/types/filter/defocus.rst:34
msgid "Disk (to emulate a perfect circle) or Triangle (3 blades), Square (4 blades), Pentagon (5 blades), Hexagon (6 blades), Heptagon (7 blades) or Octagon (8 blades)."
msgstr "圆状（模拟一个圆形）或三角形（3片），正方形（4片），五边形（5片），六边形（6片），七边形（7片），八边形（8片）。"

#: ../../manual/compositing/types/filter/defocus.rst:38
msgid "Angle"
msgstr "角度"

#: ../../manual/compositing/types/filter/defocus.rst:37
msgid "This button is deactivated, if the Bokeh Type is set to Disk. It can be used to add a rotation offset to the Bokeh shape. The value is the angle in degrees."
msgstr "当散景类型为圆状时，此按钮无效果。可用来给散景形状添加一个旋转偏移。数值为角度值。"

#: ../../manual/compositing/types/filter/defocus.rst:40
msgid "Gamma Correction"
msgstr "伽玛校正"

#: ../../manual/compositing/types/filter/defocus.rst:41
msgid "Applies a gamma correction on the image before and after blurring it."
msgstr "在对图像进行模糊之前对图像颜色进行伽玛校正。"

#: ../../manual/compositing/types/filter/defocus.rst:46
msgid "F-Stop"
msgstr "光圈级"

#: ../../manual/compositing/types/filter/defocus.rst:43
msgid ""
"This option controls the amount of focal blur in the same way as a real camera. It simulates the aperture *f* of a real lens' iris, without modifying the luminosity of the picture. The default value 128 is assumed to be infinity: everything is in "
"perfect focus. Half the value will double the amount of blur. This button is deactivated, if *No Z-buffer* is enabled."
msgstr ""
"此选项和真实摄影机类似，用于控制光圈焦点模糊程度。它模拟真实镜头的光圈 *f* 孔，而不用修改图像的亮度信息。默认值128设定为无穷远：即所有物体都在焦点内。当数值减为原来一半，图像将产生基于原始图像效果两倍的模糊。若 *使用Z缓冲区* 选项开启，此按钮无效"
"果。"

#: ../../manual/compositing/types/filter/defocus.rst:50
msgid "Max Blur"
msgstr "最大模糊"

#: ../../manual/compositing/types/filter/defocus.rst:49
msgid "This value limits the amount of blur by setting a maximum blur radius. Could be used to optimize the performance. The default value of 0 means no limit."
msgstr "此值限定由模糊半径设置的最大值的模糊数量。可用来优化画面显示效果。默认值0含义为无限制。"

#: ../../manual/compositing/types/filter/defocus.rst:58
msgid "Threshold"
msgstr "阈值"

#: ../../manual/compositing/types/filter/defocus.rst:53
msgid "Some artifacts, like edge bleed, may occur, if the blur difference between pixels is large. This value controls how large that blur difference considered to be safe."
msgstr "如果像素之间的模糊差异过大，可能产生一些人为效果，比如边缘出血。此值控制多大的模糊差异值才是安全可靠的。"

#: ../../manual/compositing/types/filter/defocus.rst:58
msgid "Only change this value, if there is an occurring problem with an in-focus object."
msgstr "如果焦距准确的物体发生了不可预知的问题，可仅修改此值。"

#: ../../manual/compositing/types/filter/defocus.rst:61 ../../manual/compositing/types/filter/defocus.rst:142
msgid "Preview"
msgstr "预览"

#: ../../manual/compositing/types/filter/defocus.rst:61
msgid "If enabled a limited amount of (quasi-)random samples are used to render the preview. This way of sampling introduces additional noise, which will not show up in the final render."
msgstr "在渲染预览时，启用此按钮将随机采样数量减半。这种采样方式可能产生额外的杂点，但不影响最终渲染输出的结果品质。"

#: ../../manual/compositing/types/filter/defocus.rst:63
msgid "Scene"
msgstr "场景"

#: ../../manual/compositing/types/filter/defocus.rst:64
msgid "To select the linked scene."
msgstr "选择要关联的场景。"

#: ../../manual/compositing/types/filter/defocus.rst:67
msgid "No Z-buffer"
msgstr "使用Z缓冲区"

#: ../../manual/compositing/types/filter/defocus.rst:66
msgid "Should be activate for a non Z-buffer in the Z input. No Z-buffer will be enabled automatically whenever a node that is not image based is connected to the Z input."
msgstr "激活Z深度通道的无Z-缓冲区功能。当Z深度通道没有连接输入图像时，无Z-缓冲区选项自动被勾选启用。"

#: ../../manual/compositing/types/filter/defocus.rst:73
msgid "Z Scale"
msgstr "Z缩放"

#: ../../manual/compositing/types/filter/defocus.rst:70
msgid "Only active when *No Z-buffer* is enabled. When *No Z-buffer* is used, the input is used directly to control the blur radius (similar to *f-Stop* when using the Z-buffer). This parameter can be used to scale the range of the Z input."
msgstr "当 *使用Z缓冲区* 禁用时，才能使用此参数。参数用来直接控制输入的模糊半径（和使用Z缓冲区时的 *光圈级* 类似）。此参数可用来控制缩放Z深度输入值的范围。"

#: ../../manual/compositing/types/filter/defocus.rst:76
msgid "Outputs"
msgstr "输出"

#: ../../manual/compositing/types/filter/defocus.rst:79
msgid "Standard image output."
msgstr "标准化图像输出。"

#: ../../manual/compositing/types/filter/defocus.rst:83
msgid "Examples"
msgstr "范例"

#: ../../manual/compositing/types/filter/defocus.rst:88
msgid ""
"In this `blend-file example <https://wiki.blender.org/uploads/7/79/Doftest.blend>`__, the ball array image is blurred as if it was taken by a camera with an f-stop of 2.8 resulting in a fairly narrow depth of field centered on 7.5 Blender units "
"from the camera. As the balls recede into the distance, they get blurrier."
msgstr "在 `blend-file example <https://wiki.blender.org/uploads/7/79/Doftest.blend>`__, 文件中，球体阵列图像使用摄影机光圈级为2.8的值进行模糊操作，形成摄影机7.5个单位的狭小居中景深效果。球体随着距离逐渐减弱清晰度，变得模糊。"

#: ../../manual/compositing/types/filter/defocus.rst:95
msgid "No Z-Buffer Examples"
msgstr "使用Z缓冲区范例"

#: ../../manual/compositing/types/filter/defocus.rst:97
msgid ""
"Sometimes might want to have more control to blur the image. For instance, you may want to only blur one object while leaving everything else alone (or the other way around), or you want to blur the whole image uniformly all at once. The node, "
"therefore, allows you to use something other than an actual Z-buffer as the Z input. For instance, you could connect an image node and use a grayscale image where the color designates how much to blur the image at that point, where white is the "
"maximum blur and black is no blur. Or, you could use a Time node to uniformly blur the image, where the time value controls the maximum blur for that frame. It may also be used to obtain a possibly slightly better DoF blur, by using a fake depth-"
"shaded image instead of a Z-buffer. (A typical method to create the fake depth-shaded image is by using a linear blend texture for all objects in the scene or by using the \"fog/mist\" fake depth shading method). This also has the advantage that "
"the fake depth image can have anti-aliasing, which is not possible with a real Z-buffer."
msgstr ""
"有时用户想对图像的模糊程度有更多的控制。比如，仅对一个物体进行模糊而它周围物体保持原来状态不变（反之亦然），或用户想立即对整体图像进行均一化模糊。这时可以连入其他的节点作为Z深度通道的输入信息。比如用户连接一个图像节点并且使用一个灰度图来描述哪些地"
"方为模糊区域，最大模糊的地方颜色值设定为白色，无模糊区域设定为黑色。又或者用户使用时间节点来均一化模糊图像，时间值控制每帧图像的最大模糊程度。通过使用一个模拟景深明暗变化图像取代Z缓冲区，此节点也可以用来获取一个比较好的DoF（景深）模糊。（典型方法是"
"通过使用线性blender贴图或 \"fog/mist\"淡出景深明暗的方法为场景中所有物体或来创建一个模拟景深明暗图）。这种方法有个优点是可以在淡出景深图上执行反锯齿效果，这在真实的Z缓冲区上是不可能的。"

#: ../../manual/compositing/types/filter/defocus.rst:112
msgid "The parameter *No Z-buffer*, becomes then the main blur control. The input has to be scaled, because usually the value of a texture is only in the numeric range 0.0 to 1.0."
msgstr "参数 *使用Z缓冲区* ，主要进行模糊控制。输入的图像信息被缩放，因为在通常情况下贴图的纹理值在0.0到1.0范围内。"

#: ../../manual/compositing/types/filter/defocus.rst:117
msgid "Camera Settings"
msgstr "摄影机设置"

#: ../../manual/compositing/types/filter/defocus.rst:121
msgid "Distance setting in the Camera Depth of Field panel."
msgstr "摄影机景深面板距离参数设置。"

#: ../../manual/compositing/types/filter/defocus.rst:123
msgid "The *Defocus* node uses the actual camera data in your scene if supplied by a *Render Layer* node."
msgstr "若应用一个 *渲染层* 节点，*散焦* 节点将使用场景中实际摄影机数据。"

#: ../../manual/compositing/types/filter/defocus.rst:125
msgid ""
"To set the point of focus, the camera now has a *Distance* parameter, which is shorthand for Depth of Field Distance. Use this camera parameter to set the focal plane of the camera (objects Depth of Field Distance away from the camera are in "
"focus). Set *Distance* in the main *Camera* edit panel; the button is right below the *Depth of Field*."
msgstr "设置聚焦点，摄影机现在有一个 *距离* 参数，是设置景深距离的简易方法。使用此摄影机参数设置摄影机的焦点平面（物体景深距离相距焦点摄影机）。在主 *摄影机* 编辑面板设置 *距离* 参数；按钮在 *景深* 的右下角。"

#: ../../manual/compositing/types/filter/defocus.rst:132
msgid "To make the focal point visible, enable the camera *Limits* option, the focal point is then visible as a yellow cross along the view direction of the camera."
msgstr "为使焦点可见，启用摄影机 *限制* 复选框，在沿着摄影机方向出现一个黄颜色的线使焦点可视。"

#: ../../manual/compositing/types/filter/defocus.rst:137
msgid "Hints"
msgstr "提示"

#: ../../manual/compositing/types/filter/defocus.rst:140
msgid ""
"In general, use preview mode, change parameters to your liking, only then disable preview mode for the final render. This node is computationally intensive, so watch your console window, and it will give you status as it computes each render scan "
"line."
msgstr "通常，使用预览模式，依据需要改变所需参数。只有在最终渲染时是不可以使用预览的。该节点需要高强度运算，所以注意控制台窗口，这里会显示每一个渲染扫描线的实时状态信息。"

#: ../../manual/compositing/types/filter/defocus.rst:145
msgid "Edge Artifacts"
msgstr "边界设置"

#: ../../manual/compositing/types/filter/defocus.rst:145
msgid "For minimum artifacts, try to setup your scene such that differences in distances between two objects that may visibly overlap at some point are not too large."
msgstr "对于边界的最低限度，设置场景在两个物体之间可见性既重叠但一些点又不至于距离过大，使距离呈现不同的层次。"

#: ../../manual/compositing/types/filter/defocus.rst:164
msgid "\"Focus Pull\""
msgstr "“拍摄时变焦”"

#: ../../manual/compositing/types/filter/defocus.rst:148
msgid ""
"Keep in mind that this is not real DoF, only a post-processing simulation. Some things cannot be done which would be no problem for real DoF at all. A typical example is a scene with some object very close to the camera, and the camera focusing on "
"some point far behind it. In the real world, using shallow depth of field, it is not impossible for nearby objects to become completely invisible, in effect allowing the camera to see behind it. Hollywood cinematographers use this visual "
"characteristic to to achieve the popular \"focus pull\" effect, where the focus shifts from a nearby to a distant object, such that the \"other\" object all but disappears. Well, this is simply not possible to do with the current post-processing "
"method in a single pass. If you really want to achieve this effect, quite satisfactorily, here is how:"
msgstr ""
"记住这不是真实的景深，只是后期合成的模拟。对于一些物体，完全实现真实的景深可能会有困难。比较典型的范例是有一些距离摄影机比较近的物体，摄影机的焦点在一些物体后面。在真实世界中，使用浅景深，使临近物体变得完全不可见也不是不可能实现，实际上，允许摄影机"
"查看物体后面的内容。好莱坞摄影师使用这种视觉特性去实现“拍摄时变焦”的效果，摄影机焦点从附近移动到较远处，使一些不重要的物体视而不见。显然，通过单通道的后期合成方法是很难实现这种效果的，如果用户想实现此效果，比较理想的做法，如下所述："

#: ../../manual/compositing/types/filter/defocus.rst:160
msgid "Split up your scene into \"nearby\" and \"far\" objects, and render them in two passes."
msgstr "分割场景为“近处”和“远处”对象，在两个通道中分别渲染它们。"

#: ../../manual/compositing/types/filter/defocus.rst:161
msgid ""
"Now, combine the two results, each with their own \"defocus\" nodes driven by the same Time node, but with one of them inverted. (e.g. using a \"Map Value\" node with a Size of -1). As the defocus of one increases, the defocus on the other "
"decreases at the same rate, creating a smooth transition."
msgstr "现在对两个结果进行合并，每个结果带有自己的“散焦”节点并由相同的时间节点进行驱动，其中有一个时间节点是反转的。（比如使用大小为-1的“映射值”节点）当一个结果的散焦增加时，另一个结果的散焦以等比例减少，产生平滑过渡。"

#: ../../manual/compositing/types/filter/defocus.rst:178
msgid "Aliasing at Low f-Stop Values"
msgstr "低光圈级的反锯齿"

#: ../../manual/compositing/types/filter/defocus.rst:167
msgid ""
"At very low values, less than 5, the node will start to remove any oversampling and bring the objects at DoF Distance very sharply into focus. If the object is against a contrasting background, this may lead to visible stair-stepping (aliasing) "
"which OSA is designed to avoid. If you run into this problem:"
msgstr "使用比较低的光圈级的数值，比如小于5，此节点会开始移除采样过密并且在景深距离到焦点变化非常剧烈的对象。如果对象和背景对比度明显，这将使画面产生阶梯状外观（锯齿），OSA的设置用来避免此种情况的出现。若用户陷入如下问题："

#: ../../manual/compositing/types/filter/defocus.rst:172
msgid "Do your own OSA by rendering at twice the intended size and then scaling down, so that adjacent pixels are blurred together."
msgstr "采用比原图像大两倍的尺寸进行渲染，然后用自定义的OSA将渲染结果缩放回原图像实际渲染尺寸，使临近像素进行模糊融合。"

#: ../../manual/compositing/types/filter/defocus.rst:174
msgid "Use the blur node with a setting of 2 for X and Y."
msgstr "运用X和Y轴向参数为2的模糊节点。"

#: ../../manual/compositing/types/filter/defocus.rst:175
msgid "Set DoF Distance off by a little, so that the object in focus is blurred by the tiniest bit."
msgstr "稍微将景深距离设置的过一点，使在焦点上的对象看起来有些微模糊。"

#: ../../manual/compositing/types/filter/defocus.rst:176
msgid "Use a higher f-Stop, which will start the blur, and then use the Z socket to a Map Value to a Blur node to enhance the blur effect."
msgstr "使用高光圈级数值执行模糊操作，然后使用Z缓冲区连接端口到映射值节点，再连接到模糊节点以增强模糊效果。"

#: ../../manual/compositing/types/filter/defocus.rst:178
msgid "Rearrange the objects in your scene to use a lower-contrast background."
msgstr "使用低对比度背景重新排列场景中的物体对象。"

