#: ../../manual/compositing/types/filter/defocus.rst:181
msgid ""
"A final word of warning, since there is no way to detect if an actual Z-buffer is connected to the node, be **very** careful with the *No Z-buffer* switch. If the *Z scale* value happens to be large, and you forget to set it back to some low "
"value, the values may suddenly be interpreted as huge blur radius values that will cause processing times to explode."
msgstr "最后要提醒的一句话，如果连接到节点的Z缓冲区无法被检测到，要非常小心的启用“使用Z缓冲区”开关。如果 *Z缩放* 值过大，用户又忘记将其设置回较低的数值，这个较大的数值会导致突然解释为较大的模糊半径并在合成时产生突然激增的后果。"
